# Scheduling Algorithms (PhD Grade)

## Benchmarking & Data
- **Standard Traces:** Google Cluster, Alibaba Trace, CloudSim.
- **Pareto Frontier:** Use for multi-objective (Makespan vs Energy).
- **Statistical Significance:** Always use t-tests/ANOVA for results.

## Complexity & Scalability
- Verify Time Complexity ($O(n^2 \times m)$).
- Test scalability up to 10,000+ tasks.

## Research Guardrails
- Avoid cherry-picking; show worst-case scenarios.
- Disclose all hyper-parameters (mutation rates, etc.).
- Use consistent, strong baselines.
